"露娜在雨中捡到一只小狗，躲在长椅下发抖。她把它带回家，但妈妈说不能养宠物。露娜很难过，贴了“招领”海报。第二天，一位老太太来敲门——原来是小狗的主人！她很感激，送给露娜一份手写曲奇配方。从此露娜每周都会去看望她，小狗每次见到她都摇尾巴。" = "Luna found a puppy in the rain, trembling under a bench. She brought it home, but her mom said they couldn’t keep pets. Luna was sad and put up “found” posters. The next day, an old lady knocked—she was the puppy’s owner! She was grateful and gave Luna a handwritten cookie recipe. From then on, Luna visited her every week, and the puppy always wagged its tail when it saw her.";
